727376f-a.text:
Merrick Boulevard, east side, between Liberty and 104th Avenues, showing two combined frame dwellings with entrances at both ends.  Note the barn to the left of the house.

P. L. Sperr

March 30, 1932
727376f-a.folder: Merrick Boulevard & Liberty Avenue, Queens, NY

727215f-b.text:
Liberty Avenue, at the S.E. corner of Merrick Boulevard.  This property was owned by A. Jordan in 1891 and Liberty Avenue, at this point, was then South Street.

P. L. Sperr

March 30, 1932
